        style="it">perfect </char>based on the occurrence of the same word in v. 12; Meyers says it means morally
        mature. This is due to Paul including himself in saying <char style="it">may we be</char> a couple words
        later, when he said he’s not perfect in v. 12.</char>
    </note>
